sectionHeading: The Lexington Traffic Management Center will be closed on Monday September 5 for Labor Day.  Regular traffic reports will resume Tuesday September 6 at 6:30 a.m.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for Tates Creek Rd
location: Outbound Tates Creek Rd CLOSED by Turkey Foot Rd until approximately 3 p.m. due to electrical pole damage from an earlier collision.
